comments Auburn beat writers discuss magntiude of Kentucky game Auburn beat writers discuss magnitude of Kentucky game How crucial is Thursday's game at Kentucky? Auburn beat writers Wesley Sinor and James Crepea share their thoughts. (Wesley Sinor/AL.com) Comments 
Gus Malzahn is looking to right the ship with a win over Kentucky on Thursday. Is this the turning point for Auburn's season? 
Tiger beat writers Wesley Sinor and James Crepea share their thoughts in the video above. Stay tuned to AL.com Thursday morning for their score predictions.
